import React from 'react';
import NavBar from './components/Navbar'
import "./App.css"
import {BrowserRouter, Browserrouter,Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './components/screens/Home'
import Profile from './components/screens/Profile'
import Login from './components/screens/Login'
import Signup from './components/screens/Signup'

  function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <NavBar/>
      <Route path="/">
        <Home/>
      </Route>
      <Route path="/signin">
        <Signin/>
      </Route>
      <Route path="/signup">
        <Signup/>
      </Route>
      <Route path="/profile">
        <Profile/>
      </Route>
    </BrowserRouter>
    
  );
}

export default App;
